item.title: Tama Tonga: From the Indies to WWE SmackDown
item.description: Alipate Aloisio Leone, better known by his ring name Tama Tonga, has left an indelible mark on the world of professional wrestling. From his early days on the independent circuit to his recent debut in WWE, let's explore the fascinating journey of this Tongan powerhouse.

item.title: The Ultimate Guide to Trying Out for WWE's Performance Center
item.description: So you want to be a pro wrestler / sports entertainer for the biggest wrestling company in the world? They actually made it easy for you to join and train at the world famous PC, aka the WWE Performance Center, located in Orlando, Florida. WWE (World Wrestling Entertainment) is constantly looking for fresh talent and even created a website to make the process easier. Scroll down to learn more!
